headline: Trump Has Put Solar In Limbo. What It Means for First Solar, Enphase, Sunrun Earnings.
summary: Key themes heading into earnings include tariffs, IRA uncertainty, demand for residential solar, and what Trump’s policies will mean for interest rates.
